\/p95VHY-1L6","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":19399,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/06\/23\/dajjal-false-messiah-khawarij\/","url_meta":{"origin":6764,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Dajjal: False Messiah will emerge from Khawarij","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 23, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cPeople will appear who recite the Quran but it will not go beyond their throats. Every time a faction emerges it will be cut off.\u201d I heard the Prophet say this more than ten times until\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32435,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/22\/ibn-umar-strict-adherence\/","url_meta":{"origin":6764,"position":1},"title":"Ibn Umar on Sunnah: Ibn Umar\u2019s strict adherence to the Prophet\u2019s actions","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 22, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Mujahid reported: We were with Ibn Umar, may Allah be pleased with him, on a journey. We passed by a place and he kept to the side away from it. He was asked, \u201cWhy did you do that?\u201d Ibn Umar said, \u201cI saw the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14295,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/19\/sunnah-umar-or-prophet\/","url_meta":{"origin":6764,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sunnah: Are you commanded to follow Umar or the Prophet?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 19, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Salim reported: A man from Syria asked Abdullah ibn Umar, may Allah be pleased with him, about continuing after Umrah to Hajj. Ibn Umar said, \u201cIt is lawful.\u201d The man said, \u201cBut your father prohibited it.\u201d Ibn Umar said, \u201cIs the command to follow my father or the Messenger of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11062,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/06\/always-believers-obedient\/","url_meta":{"origin":6764,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Faith: There will always be righteous believers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu 'Inabah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah will continue to cultivate in this religion those He uses to act in obedience to Him.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 8 Grade:\u00a0Hasan\u00a0(fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0639\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32437,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/22\/ibn-umar-as-prophet-napped\/","url_meta":{"origin":6764,"position":4},"title":"Ibn Umar on Sunnah: Ibn Umar naps as the Prophet napped","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 22, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Nafi\u2019 reported: Ibn Umar, may Allah be pleased with him, would come to a tree between Mecca and Medina, and he would take a nap under it. He told people that the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, had done so. Source: Musnad al-Bazza\u0304r 1519 Grade: Hasan (fair) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36488,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/06\/01\/supporters-of-oppression\/","url_meta":{"origin":6764,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dhulm: Allah angry with helpers of injustice","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 1, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever supports a disputant in wrongdoing, or helps in wrongdoing, he will be subject to the wrath of Allah until he removes himself.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 2320 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhad